comments: Horford (BOS) is in the paint and actively guarding an opponent throughout the possession.
Tatum (BOS) clears space from Curry (BKN) off ball and the contact does not affect his defensive position.
Irving (BKN) makes marginal contact with Smart's (BOS) side body during his drive to the basket and shot attempt. Any additional contact to Smart's arm is inconclusive.
Dragic (BKN) makes marginal contact to Brown's (BOS) body at the end of his drive that doesn't affect his SQBR.

Tatum (BOS) makes incidental contact with Durant's (BKN) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt or his ability to follow through. Any contact on the elbow prior to the shot attempt is inconclusive.
Dragic (BKN) makes contact to Brown's (BOS) body at the start of his drive that affects his SQBR.
Smart (BOS) swipes down and makes contact with Claxton's (BKN) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Curry (BKN) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Dragic (BKN) briefly wraps and releases Tatum's (BOS) body off ball and the contact doesn't affect his FOM.
Dragic (BKN) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Brown (BOS) makes marginal contact to Durant's (BKN) body that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
